Firstly, it&#8217;s crucial to understand the difference between medical and recreational marijuana. Medical marijuana uses the same plant as recreational, but it&#8217;s taken for managing certain medical conditions.<br />
The marijuana plant contains many chemicals, but two are of significant medical interest: THC (delta-9-tetrahydrocannabinol) and CBD (cannabidiol). THC &#8230;</p>
